$Packages$magrittr$Description
[1] "Provides a mechanism for chaining commands with a new forward-pipe operator, %>%. This operator will forward a value, or the result of an expression, into the next function call/expression. There is flexible support for the type of right-hand side expressions. For more information, see package vignette.  To quote Rene Magritte, \"Ceci n'est pas un pipe.\""

