$Packages$S4Arrays
$Packages$S4Arrays$Package
[1] "S4Arrays"

$Packages$S4Arrays$Version
[1] "1.10.1"

$Packages$S4Arrays$Source
[1] "Bioconductor"

$Packages$S4Arrays$Title
[1] "Foundation of array-like containers in Bioconductor"

$Packages$S4Arrays$Description
[1] "The S4Arrays package defines the Array virtual class to be extended by other S4 classes that wish to implement a container with an array-like semantic. It also provides: (1) low-level functionality meant to help the developer of such container to implement basic operations like display, subsetting, or coercion of their array-like objects to an ordinary matrix or array, and (2) a framework that facilitates block processing of array-like objects (typically on-disk objects)."

